.TH CORTEX-STATUSLINE 1 "2026-03-27" "cortex-statusline 2.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
cortex-statusline \- Command-line tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cortex-statusline
[IOPTIONS...R]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cortex-statusline
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show help message and exit
